---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/ui/PageHero";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — CyberAIQ" description="CyberAIQ AG Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, store, protect, and disclose information.">
  <PageHero client:load variant="contact" title="Privacy Policy" />

  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 md:px-10">
      <div class="legal-content space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>We are committed to protecting the privacy, confidentiality, and security of personal and business information collected through our digital platforms. This Cyber Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, protect, and disclose information in compliance with applicable data protection and cybersecurity laws.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, company name, job title</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, operating system</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on the website, interactions with forms</li>
            <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Emails, inquiries, and support requests</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
          <p>Collected information is used to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
            <li>Respond to inquiries and customer requests</li>
            <li>Process orders, contracts, or service agreements</li>
            <li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li>
            <li>Ensure cybersecurity, fraud prevention, and system integrity</li>
            <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>4. Data Protection & Cybersecurity Measures</h2>
          <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures, including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Secure servers and encrypted data transmission</li>
            <li>Access control and authentication mechanisms</li>
            <li>Regular system monitoring and vulnerability assessments</li>
            <li>Firewalls, malware protection, and intrusion detection</li>
            <li>Restricted access to personal data on a need-to-know basis</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Despite best efforts, no digital system is completely secure; however, we continuously enhance our safeguards.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>5. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p>Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Improve website performance</li>
            <li>Analyze traffic and usage patterns</li>
            <li>Remember user preferences</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Users may control or disable cookies through browser settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>6. Data Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
          <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or rent personal data. Information may be shared only:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>With trusted service providers under confidentiality agreements</li>
            <li>When required by law, regulation, or legal process</li>
            <li>To protect our rights, security, or property</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or to comply with legal obligations.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>8. User Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on applicable laws, users may have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access their personal data</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent</li>
            <li>Object to certain data processing activities</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Requests can be made by contacting us using the details below.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>Our website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of third-party sites.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>10. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>This Cyber Privacy Policy may be updated periodically to reflect changes in technology, laws, or business practices. Updates will be posted on this page.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>11. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>For questions, concerns, or privacy-related requests, please contact:</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@cyberaiq.com" class="text-[#F97316] hover:underline">contact@cyberaiq.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Company Name:</strong> CYBERAIQ AG</p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> Cloud Spaces – Circle Mall, Cloud Suite 314 Circle Mall – 2nd Floor, Jumeirah Village Circle</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .legal-content h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.75rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(240, 244, 248, 0.93);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .legal-content p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .legal-content strong {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .legal-content ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
    }
    .legal-content li {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .legal-content li::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.65em;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.6);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
